Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.81,0:25:52.45,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.28,0:25:59.22,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,鳴り止まない
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.14,0:26:07.80,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,spin-the-brand-new-lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:12.48,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,今も　ずっと
